    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014it\u2019s in stunning, like-new condition and has been kept tucked away in a garage since day one. Not a single scratch or dent to be found, and the interior still smells brand new! It drives like an absolute dream and truly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been pampered and loved, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
